#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:84
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"rk_weaponlike\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The RadiKal Bam make these by applying electroshocks to a technopath bathed in acid and stuffed with a bomb, making it mad and unable to change shape but capable of bomb-launching. No longer counts as a technopath or morph.\n"
"\n"
"\tInherited stats: takes 0.5 crew slot, immune to suffocation, 75% resistance to fire damage and stun, 0.8x movement speed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:88
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"rk_weaponlike\"]/title"
